clusters_with: bone-pile-small, bone-charm, fang-scatter, feather-bundle, animal-skull
notes: A tiny animal skull (bird/rat/fox size) lying on the ground — ritual curio or natural detritus. Floor scatter for witchy or feral areas. Unlike animal-skull and skull-small this is deliberately minimal, good for dense scatter.
